@startuml Parkinson_Prediction_Workflow
title Parkinson's Disease Prediction System - End-to-End Workflow\n(Upload -> Feature Extraction -> Prediction)

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontColor black
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor white
skinparam ActivityBorderColor black
skinparam PartitionBorderColor black
skinparam PartitionBackgroundColor white

|**User / Client**|
start
:User chooses input type;
note right: Audio OR Handwriting image OR Gait video OR Combined video

|**Upload and Validation**|
if (Input type?) then (Audio)
  :POST /api/upload/audio;
  :Validate file, extension, size;
elseif (Handwriting)
  :POST /api/upload/handwriting;
  :Validate file, extension, size;
elseif (Gait video)
  :POST /api/upload/gait;
  :Validate file, extension, size;
else (Combined video)
  :POST /api/process_combined_video;
  :Validate video + flags;
endif

if (Validation OK?) then (yes)
  :Continue;
else (no)
  :Return 400 error;
  stop
endif

:Save file to temporary path;

|**Feature Extraction**|
if (Modality?) then (Voice)
  :Extract Voice - 22 features;
  :Return speech_features;
elseif (Handwriting)
  :Extract Handwriting - 10 features;
  :Return handwriting_features;
elseif (Gait)
  :Extract Gait - 10 features;
  :Return gait_features;
else (Combined)
  fork
    :Extract audio to WAV; Speech -> 22 values;
  fork again
    :Extract middle frame; Handwriting -> 10 values;
  fork again
    :Gait from video -> 10 values;
  end fork
  :Merge all features;
endif

:Delete temporary files;
:Return JSON with features;

|**User / Client**|
:Client receives features;
:Client calls Predict;

|**Prediction API**|
:POST /api/predict;
:Body: speech, handwriting, gait features;

:Validate at least one modality;
if (Counts correct?) then (yes)
  :Counts OK;
else (no)
  :Return 400;
  stop
endif

:Build vectors;

|**Model Layer**|
if (DL model available?) then (yes)
  :Advanced AI - SE-ResNet + Attention;
  :Return label, confidence, probabilities;
else (no)
  :ML fallback - SVM/LR;
  :Return label, confidence, probabilities;
endif

|**Prediction API**|
:Save to DB if authenticated;
:Return 200 JSON result;

|**User / Client**|
:Display result to user;
stop

@enduml

' =============================================================================
' Diagram 2: Video to Gait - Extraction Steps (B&W)
' =============================================================================
@startuml Gait_Extraction_Detail
title Video to Gait - Extraction Steps

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontColor black
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor white
skinparam ActivityBorderColor black

start
:Walking video;
:Open video, read frames (max 300);
:Grayscale and blur;
:Frame difference -> motion per frame;
:Array of motion values;
:Detect steps (peaks);
:Step intervals -> stride_interval, stride_interval_std;
:Swing and stance from motion;
:Cadence, gait_speed, step_length;
:stride_regularity, gait_asymmetry;
:Return 10 gait features;
stop

@enduml

' =============================================================================
' Diagram 3: Image to Handwriting - Extraction Steps (B&W)
' =============================================================================
@startuml Handwriting_Extraction_Detail
title Image to Handwriting - Extraction Steps

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontColor black
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor white
skinparam ActivityBorderColor black

start
:Handwriting or drawing image;
:Load, grayscale, binarize;
:Stroke widths -> mean_pressure, std_pressure;
:Contour smoothness -> velocity, acceleration;
:Connected components -> pen_up_time;
:Stroke length, writing_tempo;
:Skeleton and line fit -> tremor_frequency;
:Smoothness + tremor -> fluency_score;
:Return 10 handwriting features;
stop

@enduml
